<plot>This road-movie style documentary takes a candid look at "The American Dream" through the words of its interviewees which range from preacher to poet. Combining these interviews with footage often shot from the hip and a soundtrack of contemporary music from Pascal Lamour, Tori Kami, Venus de Rides and the poetry of Craig B. Snyder, this film asks more questions than it gives answers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119812</url></doc>
